~\\displaystyle\\int^{-8}_{0}\\left(-4x^\\frac13\\right)\\,dx\n\\\\&=(-3x^\\frac43)\\Bigg|^\\blueD{-8}_{\\maroonD0}\\end{align}$", "Second, plug in the limits of integration:\n\n$[-3\\cdot(\\blueD{-8})^{\\frac43}]-[-3\\cdot\\maroonD0^{\\frac43}] = -48-0 = -48$.", "The answer:\n\n$\\displaystyle\\int^{-8}_{0}\\left(-3\\sqrt[3]{x}\\right)\\,dx~=~-48$"], "widget_types": ["numeric-input"], "answer_data": {"numeric-input 1": {"type": "numeric-input", "answers": [{"maxError": null, "message": "", "simplify": "required", "status": "correct", "strict": false, "value": -48}]}}}, {"item_id": "a3723d5f73865b288cf6c495e3f876f1", "question_content": "**Evaluate the definite integral.**\n\n$\\displaystyle\\int^{-1}_{0}\\left(-16\\sqrt[3]{x}\\right)\\,dx = $ [[☃ numeric-input 1]]", "hints": ["First, use the power rule:\n\n$\\begin{align}\\displaystyle\\int^{-1}_{0}\\left(-16\\sqrt[3]{x}\\right)\\,dx~&=~\\displaystyle\\int^{-1}_{0}\\left(-16x^\\frac13\\right)\\,dx\n\\\\&=(-12x^\\frac43)\\Bigg|^\\blueD{-1}_{\\maroonD0}\\end{align}$", "Second, plug in the limits of integration:\n\n$[-12\\cdot(\\blueD{-1})^{\\frac43}]-[-12\\cdot\\maroonD0^{\\frac43}] = -12+0 = -12$.", "The answer:\n\n$\\displaystyle\\int^{-1}_{0}\\left(-16\\sqrt[3]{x}\\right)\\,dx~=~-12$"], "widget_types": ["numeric-input"], "answer_data": {"numeric-input 1": {"type": "numeric-input", "answers": [{"maxError": null, "message": "", "simplify": "required", "status": "correct", "strict": false, "value": -12}]}}}, {"item_id": "232354be0ab25ef4a930094e9d9a8406", "question_content": "**Evaluate the definite integral.**\n\n$\\displaystyle\\int^{-1}_{27}\\left(-8\\sqrt[3]{x}\\right)\\,dx = $ [[☃ numeric-input 1]]", "hints": ["First, use the power rule:\n\n$\\begin{align}\\displaystyle\\int^{-1}_{27}\\left(-8\\sqrt[3]{x}\\right)\\,dx~&=~\\displaystyle\\int^{-1}_{27}\\left(-8x^\\frac13\\right)\\,dx\n\\\\&=(-6x^\\frac43)\\Bigg|^\\blueD{-1}_{\\maroonD{27}}\\end{align}$", "Second, plug in the limits of integration:\n\n$[-6\\cdot(\\